ubuntu-docviewer-app (2.0) vivid; urgency=medium

  [ Alan Pope ]
  * Use a confined template when running on phones

  [ Roman Shchekin ]
  * Performance improvements in LibreOffice viewer
  * Multithreading support in LibreOffice viewer
  * Get screen DPIs at runtime.
  * Asynchronous LibreOffice viewer loading
  * LibreOffice viewer render engine
  * Support for LibreOffice documents
  * LibreOffice viewer: added pinch-to-zoom gesture (LP: #1514460)

  [ Nicholas Skaggs ]
  * Fix internet check for 'get-click-deps' script when running on jenkins.

  [ Stefano Verzegnassi ]
  * Don't import a second copy of a document using ContentHub (LP: #1432394)
  * Use ContentHub QML APIs (LP: #1469422)
  * Updated to Qt 5.4 and Ubuntu.Components 1.2 (LP: #1470897)
  * Added share option (LP: #1494818)
  * UI updates
  * Removed GridView from documents page
  * Refactored app initialization
  * Refactored project folders
  * Automatically fetch LibreOffice dependencies when building a .click package
  * Updated app icons (LP: #1476659)
  * Performance improvements in LibreOffice viewer
  * Zoom implementation in LibreOffice viewer
  * Support for LibreOffice documents
  * Improved support for LibreOffice Presentation documents
  * Disable file locking in LibreOffice (LP: #1517074)
  * Added error detection in LibreOfficeViewer (LP: #1514458)
  * Fixed broken SHOW_TILE_BORDER mode (LP: #1515037)
  * LibreOffice viewer: Fix wrong size for last tile in a row/column (LP: #1516239)
  * LibreOffice viewer: Don't create tiles outside the visible/buffer grid (LP: #1516241)
  * Refactored project structure
  * Updated to Ubuntu.Components 1.3 (ubuntu-sdk-14.04.1) (LP: #1508363)
  * Better zoom support on desktop
  * Changed header behaviour in the PDF viewer (LP: #1453403)
  * LibreOffice viewer: Fix for slide navigation buttons obscured by bottom edge tab (LP: #1513843)

 -- Stefano Verzegnassi <verzegnassi.stefano@gmail.com>  Sat, 28 Nov 2015 13:30:55 +0100

